  <aspecttable>SE TSFS 2010</aspecttable>
  <name>Shunting signal, dwarf signal</name>
  <reference>See wikipedia <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swedish_railway_signalling">Swedish railway signaling</a>
  for english information.</reference>
  <description>A dwraf signal to be used inside the station to control shunting movements.
  Shunting movements take place between this signal and next dwarf signal or "end of shunting" signal.</description>
  
